    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（クォーターファイナル。これに勝つと次は）\n（サニーピースはTRINITYAiLEと）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(We’re in the quarter-finals. If we win‚ the next round‚)\n(Sunny Peace will go up against TRINITYAiLE‚)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.333333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（月のテンペストは）\n（LizNoirと当たることになる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(and Moon Tempest)\n(will go up against LizNoir.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.566666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "04-2d",
      "startTime": 11.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……本当に良かったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you sure you’re okay with this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "はい。別に喧嘩した訳じゃないですから……\n今は、そういうのが必要な時期なんだと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. It’s not like we had a disagreement or anything‚\nbut I think we’re at a stage where it’s for the best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.666666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-3d",
      "startTime": 22.966666666666665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい、{user}さんを見ると\nどうしても麻奈さんのことを考えてしまって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry‚ {user}… but whenever I look at you‚\nI can’t help but think of Mana.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（さくらには、自分の歌を探すことに集中してほしい）\n（だから俺は今日まで、さくらとの接触を避けていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I want Sakura to focus on finding her own song.)\n(So I’ve been avoiding contact with Sakura leading up to today.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "04-2d",
      "startTime": 40.166666666666664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（その時、視界に一人の男が飛び込んできた）\n（バンプロの社長、朝倉だ。神崎莉央もいる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Just then‚ a man appears in my field of vision.)\n(It’s Van Productions’ president‚ Asakura. Rio Kanzaki is with him.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "朝倉……敵情視察か。関係者席にはトリエルの面々も",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Asakura… here to spy on the enemy? I also saw people from TRINITYAiLE",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いたな……それだけ警戒されているということだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "in the official guest seats… I guess that goes to show how wary they are of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.06666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 62.86666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 62.86666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_achieve-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 63.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "さくら……みんな\n本当にごめん。私のワガママで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura… girls…\nI really am sorry for being so selfish.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 71
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん……\nううん。平気だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono…\nIt’s okay. We’re fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 75.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "（あの日、琴乃ちゃんは私に言った。一度でいい）\n（麻奈さんの声で、彼女の遺した歌を歌ってほしいと）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(That day‚ Kotono told me: “I don’t care if it’s just once‚)\n(please let me hear the song Mana left behind in her voice.”)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 86.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、曲を変更したいと聞いた時は\n何を言い出すのかと思ったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll admit‚ when you said you wanted to change the song‚\nI thought you were out of your mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 93.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "（私は琴乃ちゃんの願いを受け入れた。そうしないと）\n（自分の歌は見つからない。そんな気がしたから）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I agreed to Kotono’s request. If I hadn’t‚)\n(I had the feeling I’d never be able to find my own song.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 103.16666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "（突然の話だったけど、サニピのみんなは）\n（驚きながらも快く受け入れてくれた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Even though it was a sudden change‚ everyone in Sunny Peace)\n(willingly accepted the request‚ despite their surprise.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 109.86666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "私は光栄です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m honored.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 112
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "私は、ずっと賛成していたよ\n心配しないで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve always been on board.\nDon’t worry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 117.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "この歌なら……勝てる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With this song… we can surely win.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 120.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
