    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "俺はあの子達に本気で勝ってほしいと思っている。よく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I seriously do want those girls to win. I don’t want",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "健闘しました、ではなくだ。でも、今のままではダメだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "to give them a consolation speech. But… they’re not ready yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "歌を自分のものに出来るか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can they make that song their own?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_05-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈も同じことを言っていた。もし出来なければ）\n（ここで勝っても、セミファイナルでは勝てない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Mana said the same thing. If they can’t do it‚)\n(even if they win the quarter-finals‚ they can’t win the semi-finals.)",
